    |      |                                   |
    |      V                                   |
    +------------------------------------------+
    |                                          |
    |   Some basic data and measures to help   |
    |   game design work without callbacks.    |
    |   ( Conceptualy, in any order )          |
    |                                          |
    |   +   FILEBOI  : File Access Functions   |
    |   +   NATIKEY  : Native Keyboard Funcs   |
    |                                          |
    |   +   IKEYBOX  : Input Keyboard Values   |
    |   +   IMOUBOX  : Input Mouse    Values   |
    |                                          |
    |   +   CEDITOR  : Current Editor In Focus |
    |                                          |
    +------------------------------------------+
    |                                          |
    |   Windows & Dialogs Section              |
    |                                          |
